text: Ponciano Contreras (born 16 April 1947) is a Mexican wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 63 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Mexico Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Durango
